ates and characterises only the higher redshift regime (z > 0.45), which\nprobably implies a significant and recent evolution of the isolation status of\nthe most isolated and most massive haloes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 May 2018 16:09:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 May 2018 11:07:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
