esponsible for intrinsic low lattice\nthermal conductivities. Our results present a novel strategy of designing\nhigh-performance thermoelectric materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 May 2018 17:15:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-06"}
