ry\nblack hole population. All of the tools described in this work are publicly\navailable and ready-to-use to interpret real or synthetic LIGO data, and to\nsynthesize projected data from future observing runs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 May 2018 17:47:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Apr 2019 19:08:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 16 Aug 2019 21:56:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-20"}
