ved. We demonstrate that injecting the terminal momentum of SNe, a\npopular sub-grid model in the literature, fails to capture SN winds\nirrespective of the inclusion of residual thermal energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 May 2018 06:25:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Oct 2018 23:33:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Nov 2018 21:04:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-12"}
